      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The United States continues to maintain a robust military posture with ongoing operations against Iran&#39;s missile and nuclear programs. The Navy&#39;s Gerald R. Ford carrier strike group is engaged in exercises and training activities in the Mediterranean Sea, while the amphibious America LHD-2 participates in landings and support missions near Hawaii. Destroyer Porter is active in anti-submarine warfare exercises off California, and cruiser Ticonderoga conducts anti-aircraft and anti-surface warfare operations in the Gulf of Mexico.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
